install geckodriver
 - download latest (at the time of writing https://github.com/mozilla/geckodriver/releases/tag/v0.24.0)
 - unpack to current directory (it can also be in the PATH elsewhere)
install firefox

note: the images are pushed as base64 encoded image tags. This is pushing discourse - the default
maximum post is 32000 bytes, and with the second image added I had to bump to double that (needed ~58k)
